atri-main (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial offline daemon for AtriStation LED matrix and ring.
  * Framebuffer auto-detection, backlight and ring LED control.
  * Input reactions: volume, mic mute, voice command button.
  * Stock boot/volume/thinking/error/mute/bluetooth/alarm/timer animations.

